{"0.32":{"start":"0.315","dur":"0.899","text":"Violence"},"1.21":{"start":"1.214","dur":"1.183","text":"and war."},"2.40":{"start":"2.397","dur":"2.831","text":"The insane brutality of ISIS continues,"},"5.23":{"start":"5.228","dur":"2.086","text":"the Russians are invading Ukraine,"},"7.31":{"start":"7.314","dur":"1.578","text":"and the Palestinians and Israelis"},"8.89":{"start":"8.892","dur":"1.598","text":"continue to slug it out."},"10.49":{"start":"10.49","dur":"2.25","text":"Does that make you feel gloomy?"},"12.75":{"start":"12.745","dur":"0.836","text":"Well"},"13.58":{"start":"13.581","dur":"0.72","text":"don&#39;t."},"14.30":{"start":"14.301","dur":"1.659","text":"Because if you look at the numbers"},"15.96":{"start":"15.96","dur":"1.26","text":"war actually seems"},"17.22":{"start":"17.22","dur":"1.32","text":"to be going out of fashion,"},"18.54":{"start":"18.54","dur":"1.52","text":"while the global population"},"20.06":{"start":"20.06","dur":"1.998","text":"is at an all time high."},"22.06":{"start":"22.058","dur":"1.312","text":"It seems that we live"},"23.37":{"start":"23.37","dur":"1.333","text":"in the most peaceful period"},"24.70":{"start":"24.703","dur":"1.361","text":"in human history."},"26.06":{"start":"26.064","dur":"1.606","text":"How is this possible?"},"27.67":{"start":"27.67","dur":"4.713","text":"(music)"},"34.07":{"start":"34.065","dur":"1.964","text":"As of September 2014,"},"36.03":{"start":"36.029","dur":"1.491","text":"there were 4 conflicts going on"},"37.52":{"start":"37.52","dur":"1.669","text":"in the world that&#39;d caused at least"},"39.19":{"start":"39.189","dur":"3.044","text":"10,000 people to die since January 2013."},"42.23":{"start":"42.233","dur":"1.449","text":"9 conflicts that killed"},"43.68":{"start":"43.682","dur":"1.434","text":"more than 1,000 people"},"45.12":{"start":"45.116","dur":"1.431","text":"and 13 that killed"},"46.55":{"start":"46.547","dur":"3.008","text":"more than 100 since January 2013."},"49.56":{"start":"49.555","dur":"1.611","text":"Not really peaceful,"},"51.17":{"start":"51.166","dur":"1.18","text":"but consider this:"},"52.35":{"start":"52.346","dur":"1.426","text":"of all the conflicts going on"},"53.77":{"start":"53.772","dur":"2.71","text":"none is an active war between countries."},"56.48":{"start":"56.482","dur":"1.957","text":"They are either civil wars"},"58.44":{"start":"58.439","dur":"1.64","text":"or local conflicts."},"60.08":{"start":"60.084","dur":"1.729","text":"Although civil wars are terrible"},"61.81":{"start":"61.813","dur":"1.659","text":"and cause huge suffering,"},"63.47":{"start":"63.472","dur":"1.79","text":"their impact is usually way smaller"},"65.26":{"start":"65.262","dur":"2.505","text":"than a war between nations or empires."},"67.77":{"start":"67.767","dur":"2.422","text":"When two nations engage in war,"},"70.19":{"start":"70.189","dur":"2.354","text":"they can mobilise much bigger forces,"},"72.54":{"start":"72.543","dur":"2.177","text":"have access to all of the state&#39;s"},"74.72":{"start":"74.72","dur":"2.135","text":"resources and logistics and"},"76.86":{"start":"76.855","dur":"2.655","text":"almost all of the population."},"79.51":{"start":"79.51","dur":"1.866","text":"So why have we transitioned from"},"81.38":{"start":"81.376","dur":"1.95","text":"wars between nation states"},"83.33":{"start":"83.326","dur":"1.624","text":"wars between nation states"},"84.95":{"start":"84.95","dur":"1.823","text":"A lot of it is to do with"},"86.77":{"start":"86.773","dur":"2.44","text":"colonialism and the cold war."},"89.21":{"start":"89.213","dur":"2.554","text":"When the cold war ended, a major driver of"},"91.77":{"start":"91.767","dur":"1.82","text":"armed conflicts vanished too."},"93.59":{"start":"93.587","dur":"1.117","text":"But the break up of the"},"94.70":{"start":"94.704","dur":"1.368","text":"communist dictatorships"},"96.07":{"start":"96.072","dur":"2.017","text":"revealed new or old tensions"},"98.09":{"start":"98.089","dur":"1.75","text":"and brought new conflicts"},"99.84":{"start":"99.84","dur":"1.309","text":"in the now freed states"},"101.15":{"start":"101.149","dur":"2.721","text":"which often resulted in civil war."},"103.87":{"start":"103.87","dur":"1.862","text":"Much more importantly,"},"105.73":{"start":"105.732","dur":"1.675","text":"in 1945,"},"107.41":{"start":"107.407","dur":"2.38","text":"nearly all of Africa, much of Asia,"},"109.79":{"start":"109.787","dur":"1.558","text":"and parts of Latin America"},"111.35":{"start":"111.345","dur":"1.726","text":"were under colonial rule."},"113.07":{"start":"113.071","dur":"1.228","text":"By 1990,"},"114.30":{"start":"114.299","dur":"3.12","text":"all but a few islands were independent."},"117.42":{"start":"117.419","dur":"0.975","text":"But wait."},"118.39":{"start":"118.394","dur":"1.657","text":"Couldn&#39;t you argue that what today&#39;s"},"120.05":{"start":"120.051","dur":"1.412","text":"multinational corporations"},"121.46":{"start":"121.463","dur":"1.233","text":"are doing in the third world"},"122.70":{"start":"122.696","dur":"2.34","text":"is just as bad as colonialism?"},"125.04":{"start":"125.036","dur":"1.653","text":"Let&#39;s look at Congo."},"126.69":{"start":"126.689","dur":"2.407","text":"It was established as a colony in 1885"},"129.10":{"start":"129.096","dur":"1.393","text":"by the Belgium king."},"130.49":{"start":"130.489","dur":"2.88","text":"An area 80 times the size of Belgium."},"133.37":{"start":"133.369","dur":"1.567","text":"Violence committed against"},"134.94":{"start":"134.936","dur":"1.271","text":"the indigenous Congolese"},"136.21":{"start":"136.207","dur":"1.336","text":"and the ruthless system of"},"137.54":{"start":"137.543","dur":"1.401","text":"economic exploitation"},"138.94":{"start":"138.944","dur":"2.45","text":"had killed about half of the population"},"141.39":{"start":"141.394","dur":"1.979","text":"by 1908."},"143.37":{"start":"143.373","dur":"2.92","text":"About 10 million Congolese were executed"},"146.30":{"start":"146.298","dur":"1.671","text":"or starved to death."},"147.97":{"start":"147.969","dur":"3.019","text":"Millions were mutilated and traumatised."},"150.99":{"start":"150.988","dur":"2.478","text":"The economic exploitation of the Congo"},"153.47":{"start":"153.466","dur":"1.808","text":"remained the top priority"},"155.27":{"start":"155.274","dur":"2.263","text":"and forced labor never really ceased"},"157.54":{"start":"157.537","dur":"2.504","text":"completely until the end of Belgium rule"},"160.04":{"start":"160.041","dur":"1.241","text":"in 1960."},"161.28":{"start":"161.282","dur":"2.921","text":"Which is not really that long ago."},"164.20":{"start":"164.203","dur":"1.174","text":"So, no."},"165.38":{"start":"165.377","dur":"1.933","text":"Colonialism was much worse than"},"167.31":{"start":"167.31","dur":"1.891","text":"vulture capitalism is today"},"169.20":{"start":"169.201","dur":"2.673","text":"and it ended just two generations ago."},"171.87":{"start":"171.874","dur":"1.287","text":"Most of the conflicts"},"173.16":{"start":"173.161","dur":"1.39","text":"that are going on right now"},"174.55":{"start":"174.551","dur":"2.155","text":"are in areas that 60 years ago"},"176.71":{"start":"176.706","dur":"2.345","text":"were under foreign control."},"179.05":{"start":"179.051","dur":"1.825","text":"But things are getting better."},"180.88":{"start":"180.876","dur":"1.851","text":"Until 1989,"},"182.73":{"start":"182.727","dur":"1.882","text":"victory for one side in a civil war"},"184.61":{"start":"184.609","dur":"0.762","text":"was common"},"185.37":{"start":"185.371","dur":"2.881","text":"while nowadays victories are much rarer."},"188.25":{"start":"188.252","dur":"1.484","text":"At the same time,"},"189.74":{"start":"189.736","dur":"2.253","text":"negotiated endings have jumped from 10%"},"191.99":{"start":"191.989","dur":"1.568","text":"to almost 40%."},"193.56":{"start":"193.557","dur":"2.167","text":"What about the rest of the world?"},"195.72":{"start":"195.724","dur":"1.561","text":"Why have nation states"},"197.29":{"start":"197.285","dur":"1.628","text":"stopped attacking each other?"},"198.91":{"start":"198.913","dur":"2.174","text":"There are 4 major reasons:"},"201.09":{"start":"201.087","dur":"0.706","text":"One."},"201.79":{"start":"201.793","dur":"1.39","text":"Democratisation."},"203.18":{"start":"203.183","dur":"1.105","text":"The steady development"},"204.29":{"start":"204.288","dur":"2.283","text":"from autocracy to democracy."},"206.57":{"start":"206.571","dur":"2.671","text":"Democracies hardly ever fight each other."},"209.24":{"start":"209.242","dur":"2.183","text":"Of all the state against state wars"},"211.43":{"start":"211.425","dur":"2.876","text":"fought since 1900, only a minority"},"214.30":{"start":"214.301","dur":"2.118","text":"were fought between democracies."},"216.42":{"start":"216.419","dur":"0.83","text":"Two."},"217.25":{"start":"217.249","dur":"1.212","text":"Globalisation."},"218.46":{"start":"218.461","dur":"2.917","text":"War is just not as effective at achieving"},"221.38":{"start":"221.378","dur":"2.502","text":"economic goals as it used to be."},"223.88":{"start":"223.88","dur":"2.146","text":"Today it&#39;s almost always cheaper"},"226.03":{"start":"226.026","dur":"1.997","text":"to buy resources on the global market"},"228.02":{"start":"228.023","dur":"2.01","text":"than to cease them by force."},"230.03":{"start":"230.033","dur":"1.779","text":"People from other nations are"},"231.81":{"start":"231.812","dur":"2.74","text":"more valuable to us alive than dead."},"234.55":{"start":"234.552","dur":"3.008","text":"Which, overall, is a pretty new concept."},"237.56":{"start":"237.56","dur":"1.064","text":"Three."},"238.62":{"start":"238.624","dur":"2.794","text":"War is so 20th century."},"241.42":{"start":"241.418","dur":"3.23","text":"Until World War I, warfare was seen as an"},"244.65":{"start":"244.649","dur":"2.235","text":"inevitable part of the human experience"},"246.88":{"start":"246.884","dur":"2.727","text":"and as a valuable tool which you could use"},"249.61":{"start":"249.611","dur":"1.624","text":"to achieve goals when diplomacy"},"251.24":{"start":"251.235","dur":"1.522","text":"hit a brick wall."},"252.76":{"start":"252.757","dur":"1.967","text":"Today we have rules that declare acts of"},"254.72":{"start":"254.724","dur":"2.24","text":"aggression illegal and stipulate that"},"256.97":{"start":"256.967","dur":"1.985","text":"armed forces is only justified in"},"258.95":{"start":"258.952","dur":"2.342","text":"self-defence or with the authority of the"},"261.29":{"start":"261.294","dur":"1.838","text":"UN Security Council."},"263.13":{"start":"263.132","dur":"2.673","text":"These rules are still broken but today"},"265.81":{"start":"265.805","dur":"2.433","text":"it&#39;s harder to do so without sparking"},"268.24":{"start":"268.238","dur":"2.111","text":"oppositions and disapproval."},"270.35":{"start":"270.349","dur":"2.301","text":"Also, we have an international court for"},"272.65":{"start":"272.65","dur":"1.647","text":"war crimes in The Hague."},"274.30":{"start":"274.297","dur":"3.026","text":"And that&#39;s a very recent innovation."},"277.32":{"start":"277.323","dur":"0.99","text":"Four."},"278.32":{"start":"278.318","dur":"2.398","text":"Borders are mostly fixed now."},"280.72":{"start":"280.716","dur":"1.536","text":"After World War II,"},"282.25":{"start":"282.252","dur":"2.2","text":"territorial wars generally stopped"},"284.47":{"start":"284.468","dur":"1.913","text":"when most countries pledged to accept"},"286.38":{"start":"286.381","dur":"1.06","text":"international borders"},"287.45":{"start":"287.45","dur":"2.569","text":"and respect other nations autonomy."},"290.02":{"start":"290.019","dur":"2.026","text":"But is all of this just an anomaly"},"292.05":{"start":"292.045","dur":"2.449","text":"or are we on the road to lasting peace?"},"294.49":{"start":"294.494","dur":"0.8","text":"Truth is"},"295.29":{"start":"295.294","dur":"1.43","text":"we don&#39;t know yet."},"296.72":{"start":"296.724","dur":"1.626","text":"We need a big enough sample to rule out"},"298.35":{"start":"298.35","dur":"1.677","text":"the historical average, which is about"},"300.03":{"start":"300.027","dur":"1.902","text":"one or two big wars per century."},"301.93":{"start":"301.929","dur":"1.73","text":"We just haven&#39;t had enough time since"},"303.66":{"start":"303.659","dur":"2.073","text":"World War II to rule out the possibility"},"305.73":{"start":"305.732","dur":"1.72","text":"that war is not going away."},"307.45":{"start":"307.452","dur":"1.716","text":"If we don&#39;t have one major war"},"309.17":{"start":"309.168","dur":"1.724","text":"in the next 75 years,"},"310.89":{"start":"310.892","dur":"1.503","text":"we can be really confident"},"312.40":{"start":"312.395","dur":"1.827","text":"that humanity is changing."},"314.22":{"start":"314.222","dur":"2.944","text":"So you see, war might be over."},"317.17":{"start":"317.166","dur":"1.734","text":"Yes there are nasty conflicts"},"318.90":{"start":"318.9","dur":"2.067","text":"going on in many places but overall,"},"320.97":{"start":"320.967","dur":"1.393","text":"things are getting better."},"322.36":{"start":"322.36","dur":"1.406","text":"And we can make them even better"},"323.77":{"start":"323.766","dur":"3.627","text":"by speaking up for peace and democracy."},"343.00":{"start":"343","dur":"3","text":"Subtitles by the Amara.org community"}}